choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today presuming no dietary restrictions.
Sure, here's a sample meal plan for you today that includes breakfast, lunch and dinner options with their respective calorie counts: 
Breakfast: 
- Oatmeal (1/2 cup) with sliced almonds, honey, and fresh berries - 304 calories
Lunch: 
- Grilled chicken salad with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, red onion, avocado, and balsamic vinaigrette dressing - 526 calories
Dinner: 
- Baked salmon fillet served with roasted vegetables (carrots, broccoli, cauliflower) and quinoa - 483 calories
Note that the above meal plan is just a sample and you may adjust it according to your preferences or dietary restrictions.
